tool_input.prompt: Count the exact number of Dune fanfiction works on AO3, identify the most popular ships/pairings, most popular characters, and most popular AU types. Look for any statistics or filtering options that show which characters and relationships are most written about.

tool_response.result:
Based on the webpage content, here are the key statistics for Dune fanfiction on Archive of Our Own (AO3):

Total Works: 1,222 Dune fanfiction works

Most Popular Characters:
1. Paul Atreides (736 works)
2. Jessica (388 works)
3. Feyd-Rautha Harkonnen (363 works)

Most Popular Relationships/Ships:
1. Paul Atreides/Feyd-Rautha Harkonnen (194 works)
2. Paul Atreides/Chani Kynes (129 works)
3. Leto Atreides I/Jessica (120 works)

Most Popular AU (Alternate Universe) Types:
1. "Alternate Universe - Canon Divergence" (159 works)
2. Arranged Marriage AUs
3. Alpha/Beta/Omega Dynamics

The filtering options reveal a diverse range of content, with works spanning different ratings, relationships, and narrative styles within the Dune universe.
